subSections.title: Glyph origin
subSections.text:
Variant of {{zh-l|*別}}, where {{zh-l|*𠮠}} is replaced with the visually-similar {{zh-l|*另}}.

Officially adopted as the simplified form of {{zh-l|*彆}} in the ''Chinese Character Simplification Scheme'' ({{w2|zh|pref=《|s:漢字簡化方案|漢字簡化方案|suf=》}}) in 1956.
